Package: arbuilder
Title: Interactive Builder for Submission-Ready Clinical Tables
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Vignesh", "Thanikachalam", email = "about.vignesh@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Local Shiny application for building submission-ready tables,
    listings, and figures (TLFs) from ADaM clinical trial data. Provides a
    point-and-click interface that generates reproducible R scripts using
    'arframe' as the rendering engine. No server infrastructure required.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
